query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS plan_disciplines (
  id VARCHAR(36) PRIMARY KEY,
  plan_id VARCHAR(36) NOT NULL,
  discipline_id VARCHAR(36) NOT NULL,
  created_at DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  FOREIGN KEY (plan_id) REFERENCES plans(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,
  FOREIGN KEY (discipline_id) REFERENCES disciplinas(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,
  UNIQUE KEY unique_plan_discipline (plan_id, discipline_id),
  INDEX idx_plan_id (plan_id),
  INDEX idx_discipline_id (discipline_id)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_unicode_ci;
